&nbsp;
The Mascalucia Tenence Patrol after being alerted, went to a street on the northern outskirts of the country, where a man was reported as a robbery victim. On the road in a few minutes, in front of the gate of a villa on several levels, the military found a 60-year-old with a tumefied face > and the bleeding finger, which was receiving the first care from the health care of the 118. In that juncture he told that he was attacked by two boys who would reach him on a scooter, in an attempt to steal his purse, but then, after his reaction, they would attack him and beat him, until one of them would have detached him, with a bite, the phalanx of the left ring.
