In those concise moments, given the need to immediately transport the malcapitate to the hospital, the carabinieri did not ask him any further questions but asked other colleagues to follow the ambulance to the hospital and, after surgery, asked the victim further details. Meanwhile, another team of investigators immediately searched for video surveillance systems that could have recorded the scene, so as to trace back to the two robbers.
&nbsp;
However, the investigations were interrupted by the 24-year-old son of man, who, quite agitated, strangely stressed the fact that in that area there were no working cameras, trying to discourage the military in carrying out further insights. The attitude of the boy appeared very suspicious and prompted them not to leave any details. In the immediate future, therefore, all the members of the family were heard > and also the neighbors.
&nbsp;
The conflicting statements of the family nucleus have made the truth emerge. The man, in fact, had not been a victim of robbery, but, he had been misunderstood by his own son > who, at the height of a violent quarrel caused by futile motives, had also torn his finger to bite. In spite of defending his son, his father had staged the robbery, uttering his clothes on the ground and then calling both the doctors of 118 and 112. A stage in full rule: the man being denounced to the judicial authority for crime simulation, the son will face a process with the charge of serious personal injury.&nbsp;

